OL,3,CMinister announces MOT exemption for
OL,4,Csome cars to ease backlog
OL,6,FThe infrastructure minister has
OL,7,Fannounced temporary MOT exemption
OL,8,Fcertificates (TECs) for cars
OL,9,Fregistered within a certain date range
OL,10,Fto ease demand on the system.
OL,12,FJohn O'Dowd said a one-year exemption
OL,13,Fwill apply to five-year-old and seven-
OL,14,Fyear-old cars.
OL,16,FAround 115,000 cars will be eligible
OL,17,Fand the change will be for a limited
OL,18,Fperiod.
