OL,3,CMinister announces MOT exemption for
OL,4,Csome cars to ease backlog
OL,6,F"By introducing TECs, I have sought to
OL,7,Fstrike the best balance between
OL,8,Fimproving service delivery and
OL,9,Fminimising any risk to road safety,"
OL,10,Fsaid John O'Dowd.
OL,12,F"As road users we all have a personal
OL,13,Fresponsibility to behave in a way that
OL,14,Fkeeps ourselves and others safe and,
OL,15,Fregardless of TECs, it remains our
OL,16,Fresponsibility to ensure our cars are
OL,17,Fin a roadworthy condition."
