OL,6,FMr O'Dowd said he will also consider
OL,7,Flaunching a public consultation on
OL,8,Fbiennial MOT testing - testing every
OL,9,Ftwo years for private cars, light
OL,10,Fgoods vehicles, and motorcycles.
OL,12,FHowever he said this would be "subject
OL,13,Fto resources being available across
OL,14,Fthe department".
